        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Former Sri Lankan Minister Mervyn Silva was arrested by the Criminal Investigations Department on Thursday (18).",
        "The CID said that the Former Minister was arrested over the investigations taking place on an incident where Silva stormed in to the premises of the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation in Colombo in 2007.",
